    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Illari plants Captive Sun on a sightline to heal allies passing through its beam, using Outburst to reposition and Sunstruck to punish anyone who stands still under focused fire.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Her healing is a stationary beam that enemies can simply walk out of, so against a mobile enemy team her sustain output drops well below other support options.</p>\n"
